dct_title_s: Automobile routes of eastern California and Western Nevada connecting Los Angeles, Goldfield, Tonopah, Reno, and Lake Tahoe via Owens Valley
dct_description_sm: Automobile Club of Southern California ; W.L.M. ; E.J.B.
Relief shown by hachures and spot heights.
Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Oriented with north toward upper right.
Numbered 44 in bottom left annd 90 in bottom margin.
Belongs to a series of strip maps showing roads in California.
